installations
---------------
1.npm i express mongoose dotenv nodemon
2.npm i crypto-js
3.npm i jsonwebtoken
4.npm i stripe


steps
-----
1.create index.js file
2.npm init -y
3.Add start script as nodemon index.js and run npm start
4.create routes folder
5.create models folder
6.create .env file and save db string
7.cryptoJs is used to encrypt password so that it cant be seen in db(cypher AES)
8.Add a password secret key in .env file
9.Using stripe for payment